                <div
                  class="container section-title"
                  style="padding-bottom: 1px; margin-top: 0px"
                  data-aos="fade-up"
                >
                  <p>
                    <span
                      class="description-title"
                      style="font-size: 80px; font-weight: 800"
                    >
                      Giving to Others
                    </span>
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="content ps-0 ps-lg-5">
                  <p class="fst-italic">
                    A transformative realization comes when we understand that
                    our worth increases as we focus on how we can add value to
                    others. When we shift our mindset from seeking to receive
                    validation to striving to give and contribute, we cultivate
                    a deeper sense of self-worth. This focus on generosity and
                    service enriches our lives and enhances our self-esteem.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">
              <div
                class="aboutcontainer"
                style="box-shadow: rgba(99, 99, 99, 0.2) 0px 2px 8px 0px"
